OL,3,CThree sentenced after seaside attack
OL,4,Cleft man with broken ankle
OL,6,FThree men have been sentenced for a
OL,7,Fseries of attacks in Hove which left
OL,8,Fone man with a broken ankle and two
OL,9,Fothers with head injuries, after they
OL,10,Fwere punched and struck with glass
OL,11,Fbottles.
OL,13,FOn the evening of 25 November, 2022,
OL,14,Fthe three men, from west London, had
OL,15,Fbeen celebrating at the Rockwater
OL,16,Fvenue on the seafront when they became
OL,17,Finvolved in confrontations with other
OL,18,Fguests.
