OL,3,CThree sentenced after seaside attack
OL,4,Cleft man with broken ankle
OL,6,FAbdulmajid Mohamed, 30, from Chiswick,
OL,7,FFouad Al Soufah, 29, from Hounslow,
OL,8,Fand Michael Evans, 29, of Thornbury
OL,9,FRoad, Isleworth, were sentenced
OL,10,Ftogether at Hove Crown Court.
OL,12,FMohamed held two men against a marquee
OL,13,Fand Al Soufah punched one man in the
OL,14,Fface. Mohamed then hit another man in
OL,15,Fthe head.
OL,17,FAl Soufah and Evans then approached a
OL,18,F21-year-old man from Brighton leaving
OL,19,Fthe venue. They pushed him to the
OL,20,Fground and repeatedly kicked him,
OL,21,Fleaving the victim with a broken ankle.
