OL,6,FMohamed also armed himself with a
OL,7,Fheavy bottle and struck a 21-year-old
OL,8,Fman from Chichester.
OL,10,FAl Soufah was sentenced to four years
OL,11,Fin prison. Evans received a 12-month
OL,12,Fsuspended sentence, 200 hours of
OL,13,Funpaid work and was ordered to
OL,14,Fcomplete a rehabilitation programme.
OL,16,FMohamed, who failed to appear at court
OL,17,Ffor sentencing, was sentenced to six
OL,18,Fyears in prison.
